Finding ID: AR-010-SERVICING-SEAM-001
Root ID: ROOT-010-SERVICING-OWNER-SEAM

Disposition: Carried Medium

Static review confirms 010I and 010J directly import private loan schedule/allocation and
communication template/job models instead of consuming public owner facades. Their long-lived and
PostgreSQL tests also instantiate other Django TestCase classes, call setUp(), and traverse private
helpers. The assertions themselves are substantive; the architecture risk is shared setup and
policy coupling that can hide owner drift, as the changed-key review probe demonstrates.
